# thoth_mdm_sync

Starts provider sync and optionally waits for completion.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_mdm_sync" "sync" {
  provider_name       = thoth_mdm_provider.jamf.provider_name
  wait_for_completion = true
  timeout_seconds     = 180
}
```
